databaseQueries.query: SELECT * FROM `vn_district` WHERE `ProvinceID` = '' ORDER BY `name` ASC
SELECT * FROM `vn_ward` WHERE `DistrictID` = '' ORDER BY `name` ASC
SELECT `id`, `title`, `description`, `image`, `keyword` FROM `order_configs` WHERE `publish` = 0 ORDER BY `order` ASC, `id` DESC
SELECT `id`, `title`, `slug`, `image` FROM `category_products` WHERE (`alanguage` = 'vi' and `publish` = 0 and `isHeader` = 1) ORDER BY `order` ASC, `id` DESC LIMIT 6
SELECT * FROM `slides` WHERE `alanguage` = 'vi' and `slides`.`catalogueid` in (10) ORDER BY `order` ASC, `id` DESC
